Copperweld Steel Co &lt;CPSL>, asubsidiary of CSC Industries Inc., said it will increase frommarket price levels its bar, semi-finished and leaded productseffective July One.    Hot rolled and cold finished bar wil be increase 25 dlrsper net ton, while semi-finished products will be increased 15dlrs per net ton, the company said.    Anticipated higher energy and raw material costs, combinedwith current market trends, were cited by the company asreasons for the increases. Reuter&#3;